{"tid":2413051,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Facebook不再容許澳洲用戶分享新聞資訊","createTime":"2021-02-18T11:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T14:51:45.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1233965a510184d86346a1ac03caa926c387269f","tid":2413051,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:49:14.000Z","msg":"社交媒體Facebook拒絕配合澳洲政府計劃實施的一項新法例，決定不再容許澳洲用戶在旗下社交平台分享新聞資訊。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲政府準備立法，強制社交媒體使用當地傳媒的新聞內容時，向對方付費，Facebook澳洲及新西蘭經理伊斯頓批評，坎培拉政府誤解公司平台與分享新聞內容的發行者之間的關係，公司唯有採取行動，澳洲用戶將無法在Facebook閱讀或分享當地或國際新聞。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲政府表示，將會繼續與Facebook磋商。<br />\n<br />\n另一大型科企Google，較早時與傳媒大亨梅鐸成立的新聞集團達成協議，Google同意向新聞集團支付新聞內容費用。"},{"pid":"8b2d83896220c3a2892dde69734015b3e0e091e4","tid":2413051,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:49:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576132-20210218.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576132-20210218.htm&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69P5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=930d4304\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576132-20210218.htm&h=439fe365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576132-20210218.htm</a>"},{"pid":"350461aa67847cadc75a858d6921461f85a1f88d","tid":2413051,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"攬炒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1b436aec46ee8ab63db07b5290c1c47a7ca3e1","tid":2413051,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:46:54.000Z","msg":"google 又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7322d237b8d3f4c1c839bd7e2ce172de7f341aa","tid":2413051,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:47:45.000Z","msg":"facebook等收皮啦"},{"p